_sText:
fy_jibtown!

a small map made for those lazy nights when you're lanning with your friends.

has only about 10 spawns because it was really a 5 minute map.

enjoy and if you would like me to make more spawnpoints just say so.


if any of you are wondering where the random mapname came from:
there is a reference to jibtown in the bungee jumping episode of clayworld
